column9: Battleship New Jersey, Camden | pass admits 2 adults, 3 children in a family
Brooklyn Botanic Garden, Brooklyn, NY | pass admits 2 adults & accompanying children under age 16
Children's Museum of Manhattan, NYC | pass admits up to 4 people
Frick Collection, NYC | This package consists of 4 passes to the Frick Collection. Each pass admits 1 person. Children under 10 are not allowed in the galleries.
Guggenheim Museum, NYC | pass admits 4 people. Children 12 and under are free. A max of 2 additional guests are also permitted at a cost of $5.
Liberty Science Center, Jersey City | Present your Bernards Township Library Card for a 10% discount (limit one per household).  Tickets must be purchased in person to receive discount.
Montclair Art Museum Montclair | pass admits 2 adults & accompanying children
Morris Museum, Morristown | pass admits 2 adults, 3 children in a family
Museum of Early Trades & Crafts, Madison | pass admits 2 adults, 3 children in a family
New York Historical Society, NYC | pass admits 2 adults & up to 4 children under 18
Newark Museum of Art , Newark | pass admits 2 adults & children in a family

Shakespeare Theater of New Jersey, Madison | Receive 15% off tickets to the theater's 2025 season using code MAINLIB15 when buying tickets. You will need to present your library card (physically or digitally in the Main app) at the theater.
Storm King Art Center, New Windsor, NY | pass admits 2 adults & all children under age 18 living in the same household
United States Golf Association Museum, Far Hills | pass admits 4 people. Children 12 and under are free
USS Constitution Museum, Boston, MA | pass admits 9 people.  This pass has a special 8-day loan period.
